author: hughesj
msg: WODEN-109: changed jar name scheme to include "incubating" in the name and to be more consistent with other Incubator podlings by putting <version>-incubating-<milestone> in the name which facilitates posting the jars to a maven repository. So the jar names are now: woden-1.0-incubating-M6.jar woden-api-1.0-incubating-M6.jar woden-ant-1.0-incubating-M6.jar woden-test-1.0-incubating-M6.jar
